<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Elimu Pepe Parent User Journey</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="img/elimu.png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      :root {
        --primary: #0284c7;
        --primary-hover: #0369a1;
        --primary-light: #f0f9ff;
        --text-main: #0f172a;
        --text-muted: #64748b;
        --bg-page: #f8fafc;
        --bg-card: #ffffff;
        --border-color: #e2e8f0;
        --phone-frame: #0f172a;
      }
      body {
        font-family:
          "Segoe UI",
          system-ui,
          -apple-system,
          sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--text-main);
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        background-color: var(--bg-page);
      }
      header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
      }
      .logo-area {
        display: inline-flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        margin: 0 auto 14px;
        animation: bounce 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
      }
      .logo-area img {
        display: block;
        width: 84px;
        height: auto;
      }
      h1 {
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }
      .subtitle {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .platform-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        background: var(--bg-card);
        padding: 8px 18px;
        border-radius: 30px;
        color: var(--primary);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
      }
      .platform-link:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.1);
        color: var(--primary-hover);
      }
      .journey-container {
        position: relative;
      }
      .step-block {
        margin-bottom: 60px;
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border-radius: 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -15px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        overflow: hidden;
        transition:
          transform 0.3s ease,
          box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      }
      .step-block:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 30px 50px -20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
      }
      .step-layout {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 520px;
      }
      .step-info-cell {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 50px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .step-visual-cell {
        width: 440px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1f5f9 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-left: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        padding: 40px;
        position: relative;
      }
      .step-number {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        background: var(--primary-light);
        color: var(--primary-hover);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        padding: 6px 16px;
        border-radius: 100px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        width: fit-content;
      }
      .step-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: var(--text-main);
        margin: 0 0 16px 0;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }
      .step-desc {
        color: #475569;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }
      .highlight {
        color: var(--primary);
        font-weight: 600;
        background: linear-gradient(120deg, #e0f2fe 0%, #bae6fd 100%);
        padding: 2px 6px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .phone-container {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .flow-sequence {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 360px;
      }
      .flow-sequence-note {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.08);
        color: var(--primary-hover);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .flow-sequence-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 12px;
      }
      .flow-shot {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.45);
        background: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 14px 30px -18px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.35);
      }
      .flow-shot img {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
        object-fit: contain;
        background: #fff;
      }
      .flow-shot-label {
        position: absolute;
        left: 10px;
        top: 10px;
        padding: 5px 9px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.88);
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.6px;
      }
      .phone-frame {
        width: 255px;
        height: 490px;
        border: 11px solid var(--phone-frame);
        border-radius: 40px;
        background: #ffffff;
        position: relative;
        box-shadow:
          0 25px 60px -15px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.3),
          0 0 0 1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .phone-frame::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 6px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 85px;
        height: 20px;
        background: var(--phone-frame);
        border-radius: 20px;
        z-index: 30;
      }
      .phone-screen {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #ffffff;
      }
      .phone-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        display: block;
        background: #ffffff;
      }
      .missing-shot {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 24px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
        color: #475569;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.2px;
      }
      .whatsapp-float {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 20px;
  right: 20px;
  background-color: #25D366;
  color: white;
  font-size: 24px;
  padding: 15px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  text-decoration: none;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  z-index: 1000;
}

.whatsapp-float:hover {
  background-color: #1ebe5d;
}
      @keyframes bounce {
        0%,
        100% {
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateY(-6px);
        }
      }
      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .step-layout {
          flex-direction: column;
        }
        .step-visual-cell {
          width: 100%;
          border-left: none;
          border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
          padding: 50px 20px;
        }
        .step-info-cell {
          padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .flow-sequence {
          max-width: 100%;
        }
        .flow-sequence-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="logo-area">
        <img src="img/elimu.png" alt="Elimu Pepe Logo" />
      </div>
      <h1>Elimu Pepe</h1>
      <div class="subtitle"><h2>Get Started Walkthrough</h2></div>
      <a
        href="./index.html"
       
        class="platform-link"
      >
      I am a  Parent →
      </a>
    </header>

    <div class="journey-container">
      <div class="step-block">
        <div class="step-layout">
          <div class="step-info-cell">
            <div class="step-number">Step 1</div>
            <h2 class="step-title">Get The LOHO ID</h2>
            <p class="step-desc">
           
              <a
                class="highlight"
                href="https://play.google.com/store/search?q=elimu+pepe&c=apps&hl=en"
              >
                "From The Parent Account"</a
              >Your Loho ID/ Student ID  is located on your learners section like its pointed on the image.copy that for you to login .
           
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-visual-cell">
            <div class="phone-container">
              <div class="phone-frame">
                <div class="phone-screen">
                  <img
                    class="phone-image"
                    src="img/st/1a.png"
                    alt="Step 1 Surface View"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-block">
        <div class="step-layout">
          <div class="step-info-cell">
            <div class="step-number">Step 2</div>
            <h2 class="step-title">Get App From Playstore</h2>
            <p class="step-desc">
              On your Android device, open the Google Play Store and search for "Elimu Pepe" or click the link below to download the app directly. Once installed, open the app and proceed to the next step. 
              <a class="highlight"               href="https://play.google.com/store/search?q=elimu+pepe&c=apps&hl=en">"Here"</a>
          </div>
          <div class="step-visual-cell">
            <div class="phone-container">
              <div class="phone-frame">
                <div class="phone-screen">
                  <img
                    class="phone-image"
                    src="img/st/2.jpeg"
                    alt="Step 2 Action Layout"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-block">
        <div class="step-layout">
          <div class="step-info-cell">
            <div class="step-number">Step 3</div>
            <h2 class="step-title">Select "I am a Student"</h2>
            <p class="step-desc">
              Select the<span class="highlight">"I am a Student"</span>option on
              the account setup screen
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-visual-cell">
            <div class="phone-container">
              <div class="phone-frame">
                <div class="phone-screen">
                  <img
                    class="phone-image"
                    src="img/st/3.png"
                    alt="Step 3 Segment Layout"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-block">
        <div class="step-layout">
          <div class="step-info-cell">
            <div class="step-number">Step 4</div>
            <h2 class="step-title">Enter Your LOHO ID</h2>
            <p class="step-desc">
              Your Loho ID/ Student ID is located on your learners section like its pointed on step 1.
              <a class="highlight" href="https://elimupepe.loholearning.co.ke/send-password-reset-link">Forget Password click here to reset</a>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-visual-cell">
            <div class="phone-container">
              <div class="phone-frame">
                <div class="phone-screen">
                  <img
                    class="phone-image"
                    src="img/st/4.png"
                    alt="Step 4 Channel Verification"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-block">
        <div class="step-layout">
          <div class="step-info-cell">
            <div class="step-number">Step 5</div>
            <h2 class="step-title">Proceed :What Elimu Pepe Can Do</h2>
            <p class="step-desc">
  <ol class="step-list">
  <h3>🎓 Learning & Practice</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Access lessons and learning content</li>
    <li>Practice questions and exercises</li>
    <li>Take quizzes and tests</li>
    <li>Learn at their own pace</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>📊 Track Progress</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>View performance and scores</li>
    <li>Track improvement over time</li>
    <li>See completed and pending activities</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>🏆 Rewards & Motivation</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Earn points from activities</li>
    <li>Receive rewards from parents or system</li>
    <li>Stay motivated through achievements</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>🔐 Account Access</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Log in using credentials given by parents</li>
    <li>Use secure (hidden/secret) login access</li>
    <li>Access a personal learning space</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>📱 App Usage</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Use the learner mobile app</li>
    <li>Study anytime, anywhere</li>
    <li>Continue learning outside school</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>💬 Communication</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Receive messages from parents or teachers</li>
    <li>Stay updated on learning activities</li>
  </ul>

  </ol>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-visual-cell">
            <div class="flow-sequence">
              <div class="flow-sequence-note">Flow order: 5A → 5B → 5C</div>
              <div class="flow-sequence-grid">
                <div class="flow-shot">
                  <span class="flow-shot-label">5A</span>
                  <img
                    class="phone-image"
                    src="img/st/5A.png"
                    alt="Step 5A payment plan selection screen"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="flow-shot">
                  <span class="flow-shot-label">5B</span>
                  <img
                    class="phone-image"
                    src="img/st/5B.jpeg"
                    alt="Step 5B payment confirmation screen"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="flow-shot">
                  <span class="flow-shot-label">5C</span>
                  <img
                    class="phone-image"
                    src="img/st/5C.png"
                    alt="Step 5C parents dashboard redirect screen"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

<a 
  href="https://wa.me/254797349396" 
  class="whatsapp-float" 
  target="_blank"
>
  <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> 
</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
